protective chin guard and a dipped back for coverage. Stow your keys or gym pass in the handy zipped pockets.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(17,'Nike\'s \'Tech Fleece\' hooded top has a relaxed silhouette. Made from comfortable cotton-blend jersey, this style has a drawstring hood, slant pockets and thumb holes for a secure fit. It\'s ideal for winter workouts or wearing to and from the gym.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(18,'Nike\'s \'Hypercool\' shorts are cut for a sculpting fit from the label\'s sweat-wicking Dri-FIT fabric. They have breathable mesh panels and a smooth elastic waistband. Wear yours with the label\'s tank for high-impact workouts like interval training or kickboxing.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(19,'Nike\'s \'City\' T-shirt is made from Dri-FIT stretch-jersey and mesh that will keep you cool and dry during spin class or interval training. It has a longer back hem for coverage and reflective details that provide visibility in low light. Team it with black shorts.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(20,'Nike created this Dri-FIT \'Relay\' top for long-distance runs - it\'s made from breathable mesh and has zoned sweat-wicking panels that absorb perspiration. The reflective trims offer visibility in low light, while the dipped back hem provides coverage. Wear them with the brand\'s leggings.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(21,'Nike\'s Dri-FIT stretch-mesh top wicks away sweat, keeping you cool and dry during long distance runs. Strategically paneled with ventilation zones, it has flatlock seams that prevent chafing and subtle reflective trims to enhance visibility in low light.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(22,'Developed as \'all conditions gear\' for the city, Nike\'s \'NikeLab ACG\' collection is defined by technically sound materials and comfortable shapes. These stretch-cotton jersey shorts have a flexible shell waist, an array of practical pockets and zipped side slits for an adjustable fit. Team yours with sneakers and a tee from the line. Shown here with Wacko Maria hoodie, AMI T-shirt, Vans sneakers, Le Gramme bracelet.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(23,'Nike\'s \'NikeLab ACG\' collection of technical streetwear fuses form and function seamlessly. This black hoodie is made from substantial stretch-cotton jersey reinforced with piping at the hem, and has a mesh-trimmed peaked hood for ventilation. Details like thumb and headphone holes make it a practical option for city strolls or your commute. Shown here with Arc\'teryx Veilance trousers, Maison Margiela T-shirt, Nike sneakers, Arc\'teryx Veilance tote bag.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(24,'Crafted from dynamic Tech Knit fabric, this Nike bomber jacket boasts targeted ventilation in areas prone to overheating. It\'s fitted with raglan sleeves for a full range of movement and has soft ribbed trims for further insulation. Team yours with a white T-shirt and sweatpants at the weekend. Shown here with Nike T-shirt, Acne Studios trousers, Nike sneakers, Braun watch.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(25,'KENZO\'s sweatshirt is patterned with the instantly recognizable eye motif. Cut from soft cotton-jersey, this graphic style is finished with a branded patch appliqué and ribbed trims. Channel the label\'s more-is-more approach and wear yours with clashing prints.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(26,'KENZO\'s Resort \'17 collection draws inspiration from the free-spirited style of the \'90s. Made from non-stretch denim, these slim boyfriend jeans are appliquéd with playful cartoons by renowned artist Antonio Lopez. Temper the long length by rolling the cuffs and wearing yours with heeled boots.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(27,'KENZO\'s shirt dress is an off-duty staple. Made from washed-denim, it is embroidered with the label\'s iconic tiger motif and has a detachable tie that defines the waist. Wear yours layered over a sweater with sneakers.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(28,'KENZO\'s striped cotton-blend sweater is made with graphic sorbet-hued yarns. It\'s appliquéd with the label\'s signature tiger crest and trimmed with chunky ribbing. Wear yours with white jeans and sneakers.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(29,'KENZO design duo Humberto Leon and Carol Lim take inspiration from the brand\'s archives for their collections. Knitted from soft cotton-blend, this black sweater features the signature of the label\'s founder, Kenzo Takada, in a bold white intarsia. Wear yours with a patterned skirt or pants.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(30,'Creative Directors Carol Lim and Humberto Leon gave KENZO\'s Resort \'17 collection a fun, \'90s feel. Crafted from a ribbed stretch-knit, this pleated dress is paneled with swathes of color that are revealed with every move. We like it best with the season\'s fitted ankle boots.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(31,'KENZO\'s dress is cut in a timeless shape that will flatter all body types. This knitted style has a fit-and-flare design with sheer pointelle trims. We especially love this LBD paired with statement pumps.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(32,'KENZO\'s Spring \'17 runway pays tribute to its legendary show at Studio 54 in 1977. Designed to sit high on the waist, these cropped jeans are cut from dark-blue denim with an adjustable buckle at the back. Temper the exaggerated wide leg with heels.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(33,'KENZO\'s boxy denim jacket is designed to sit away from the body. Cut from rigid denim, it has dropped shoulders, voluminous sleeves and a cape-style back. Echo the Spring \'17 runway look and wear yours fully fastened over a skirt or dress.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(34,'Crafted in Italy from cotton-gabardine, Jil Sander\'s suit is representative of the brand\'s minimalist approach to contemporary tailoring. The slim-cut jacket has notch lapels, a single vent and lightly padded shoulders, and it\'s partially lined in satin with three internal pockets. Keep the trousers in place with a belt - they\'re fitted with an extra loop in the centre of the waistband that threads through the buckle to prevent them from drooping.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(35,'Diversify your denim capsule with Acne Studios\' \'Ace\' jeans. Blended with stretch for plenty of give, they\'ve been treated with the label\'s black \'Phantom\' wash and expertly faded for a cool lived-in look. The neat, skinny cut ensures they can be worn day or night. Shown here with Theory jacket, rag & bone T-shirt, Acne Studios sneakers.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(36,'TOM FORD\'s black dress proves that the simplest of designs can often be the most elegant. Cut from smoothing stretch-crepe to enhance your curves, it turns to reveal a dramatic open back, framed by a sleek gunmetal zip. Wear it to evening events with heels and a clutch.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(37,'TOM FORD\'s blazer has been expertly tailored in Italy from stretch-cady. Detailed with satin lapels and cuffs, this slim style has front pockets and is fully lined in silk to easily slip over a blouse or shirt. The single button highlights the narrowest part of your waist.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(38,'TOM FORD\'s ivory sweater is spun from the perfect blend of cashmere and silk - it feels light yet luxurious. This elegant style has a slightly loose fit and falls deliberately off one shoulder. Complement the look with a statement earring.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(39,'TOM FORD\'s dress will never go out of style. Made in Italy, this piece is spun from black cashmere that\'s enhanced with silk for added softness. It\'s designed to fit closely around the hips and falls to an elegant mid-calf length. Wear yours off one shoulder or both, depending on your mood or the occasion.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(40,'TOM FORD\'s immaculately crafted wardrobe staples are the key to elevating casual looks. Cut from garment-dyed cotton-piqué, this polo shirt is neatly embroidered with the designer\'s initials at the hem. The placket fastens with mother-of-pearl buttons - a refined detail that sets it apart, regardless of what you pair it with. Shown here with Brunello Cucinelli jeans, TOM FORD sweater, Brunello Cucinelli sneakers, TOM FORD sunglasses.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(41,'Tailoring expert TOM FORD approaches casualwear with the same exacting standards. This military-inspired shirt is crafted from dark-wash denim and fitted with epaulettes. Try yours under a field jacket, or wear it open over a striped tee.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(42,'Knitted in Italy from a beautifully soft cashmere and linen-blend, TOM FORD\'s Henley sweater typifies the commanding luxury for which the brand is renowned. The handsome mélange of storm-blue and white threads will go with almost anything in your wardrobe - try it unbuttoned over a white T-shirt in lieu of a jacket. Shown here with Ermenegildo Zegna jeans, TOM FORD T-shirt, Brunello Cucinelli sneakers, Berluti briefcase.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(43,'Mr TOM FORD\'s penchant for all things retro is evident in these Italian-made swim shorts. The smartly tailored pair is patterned with swirled tones of mustard, brown and off-white - a medley that reminds us of authentic \'60s styles. The adjustable waist tabs and neat fastening make them an adaptable option for both the pool and al fresco lunches. Shown here with TOM FORD T-shirt, TOM FORD espadrilles, Mikia bracelet.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(44,'Balenciaga\'s Spring \'17 collection explores the close ties between couture and fetishism - Demna Gvasalia spoke of his obsessive interest in achieving the perfect fit. A standout piece from the runway and one of the season\'s cult styles, these lustrous stretch-satin pants are cut for a smooth, second-skin fit and grounded by a pair of built-in stilettos. Let them peek through the slit of a midi dress or robe.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(45,'Bright colors are in the spotlight this season. From Balenciaga\'s Spring \'17 collection, this pink silk-georgette dress has a high ruched neckline, inverted back pleats and deep splits that run from the waist to the hem for beautiful movement. Style it with the label\'s skinny pants.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(46,'Block color boots and pants stole the show at Balenciaga for Spring \'17. This high-rise pink pair is cut from lustrous stretch-satin in a skinny silhouette and has discreet split cuffs - perfect for slipping over ankle boots, as spied on the runway in Paris.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(47,'Balenciaga\'s jeans are expertly crafted from blue stonewashed denim in a retro high-rise silhouette. Cut with a straight leg, this pair hits just above the ankle - perfect for teaming with boots - and has cool, exposed buttons. The pockets are washed a subtle yellow color for a worn-in look and feel.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(48,'Cut from stretch-cady, Balenciaga\'s \'One Twist\' bodysuit is designed to smooth and flatter the body. It\'s artfully draped to graze the shoulder and frame your décolletage. Wear it with everything from denim to tailoring.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(49,'Demna Gvasalia single-handedly made boxy shoulders the silhouette of the season with his Spring \'17 collection for Balenciaga. Elevating the denim jacket \"to couture sophistication,\" this piece has a structure inspired by the sharpness of a tailor\'s hanger. Made in Italy, it\'s intended to fit loosely and is finished with two breast pockets.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(50,'Give slick city attire a polished feel in Balenciaga\'s pale-blue cotton-blend poplin shirt. Immaculately crafted in Italy with a trim silhouette and sharp collar, this neatly darted piece exudes contemporary suave. Shown here with a Maison Margiela blazer and pouch, Lanvin trousers and Balenciaga shoes.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(52,'For Balenciaga\'s Spring \'17 collection, Demna Gvasalia was inspired by a coat in the label\'s archive that Mr Cristóbal Balenciaga had started to make for himself but never finished. This oversized piece is padded at the shoulders to recreate the sharpness of a hanger, and fastens with a neat fly-front - a nod to more traditional styles. It\'s been made in Italy from wool-twill that\'s substantial but not stuffy. Balance it with slim trousers. Shown here with Maison Margiela trousers, Gucci shirt, Balenciaga boots.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(53,'Balenciaga\'s dark-grey \'Blizzard\' sweater has dropped shoulders that create a flattering, relaxed profile. Illustrating the Parisian brand\'s refined and sophisticated aesthetic, this piece is expertly knitted from a naturally insulating wool-blend that feels luxuriously thick and cosy. The classic regular fit and chunky crew neck make it perfect for layering. Try yours over a black T-shirt, adding a tailored coat on particularly cold winter days.Shown here with Maison Margiela T-shirt, Valentino trousers, Dries Van Noten boots, Maison Margiela holdall.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(54,'Calvin Klein Collection\'s Spring \'17 lineup is punctuated with baby-doll silhouettes. Cut from cotton, this \'Lucinda\' dress has adjustable straps and sharp inverted pleats for volume. The exposed seams and raw edges give it a fresh, deconstructed feel.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(55,'Calvin Klein Collection\'s top is cut loose from lightweight satin-twill. The perfect addition to your workweek wardrobe, this striped design has a flattering boat neck and buttoned side slits - use the tie belt to cinch your waist. We\'ll be wearing ours with cropped jeans and pumps.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(56,'Calvin Klein Collection\'s tunic is cut from crisp cotton-poplin. This bright-white piece has an oversized fit that\'s enhanced by sharp pleating and a detachable belt to cinch your silhouette. Wear it with tailored pants to the office.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(57,'Calvin Klein Collection\'s gown proves that minimal styles can be just as exquisite and glamorous as those that are opulently embellished. This black style is cut from the smoothest silk that floats weightlessly over your body. Keep the focus on the crossover back straps with a discreet bra.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(58,'Calvin Klein Collection\'s mini dress is cut from lightweight floral-print silk-organza. Designed with a high collar, this feminine style has a nipped waist and billowy sleeves that are defined by leather-trimmed belt details. Wear yours by day with glossy boots.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(59,'Flawlessly tailored in Italy, Calvin Klein Collection\'s \'Roland\' overcoat is made from cotton-rich twill. Lightly padded shoulders and an inherent structure to the cloth enhance the smart, clean-lined profile, while the satin sleeve lining ensures it slips on easily over attire. The inky midnight-blue hue is a dapper, entirely wearable alternative to black. Shown here with Prada shirt, Calvin Klein Collection trousers, Dries Van Noten boots.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(60,'There\'s a quality to summer suiting that Calvin Klein Collection\'s \'Hudson\' blazer has in spades. The naturally puckered appearance of the silk-seersucker gives this piece a relaxed attitude. It looks equally sharp worn over a shirt or jersey tee.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(61,'Ease into the weekend wearing Calvin Klein\'s \'Romick\' sweatpants. This tapered cashmere pair has a drawstring waist and cuffed ankles. Wear them as a luxurious alternative to traditional jersey styles. Shown here with Calvin Klein Collection hoodie, Acne Studios coat, Acne Studios sneakers.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(62,'Brunello Cucinelli\'s \'Leisure\' capsule captures \"the spontaneous and rich spirit\" of the streets - a key source of inspiration for the season. This midi skirt is tailored from mushroom cotton-blend for a languid drape and finished with utilitarian canvas D-ring ties. Wear yours work to weekend, switching a white blouse for a relaxed sweater.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(63,'Brunello Cucinelli\'s maxi skirt is woven with pinstripes and finely pleated. This crisp cotton-poplin piece is made from asymmetric layers that create a full breezy shape. Accentuate the flattering black waistband with complementing accessories and a tucked-in shirt.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(64,'Brunello Cucinelli\'s jumpsuit is so effortless that you\'ll be tempted to wear it at every opportunity. Tailored from fluid ivory crepe, this tuxedo-inspired style is trimmed with lustrous silk-satin lapels and finished with an elasticated waist. Complement the cropped length with minimalist slides, switching for a more ornate pair in the evening.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(65,'Brunello Cucinelli\'s jumpsuit has been made in Italy from panels of cotton and gazar to create the illusion of separates. The wrap-effect bodice is ribbed for a close yet flexible fit and has a low-cut back, while the contrasting wide-leg pants are detailed with a waist-defining belt. We love it styled with a pair of mules.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(66,'Brunello Cucinelli is adored for his luxurious materials and classic color palettes. Blended with touches of mohair and wool, this dove-gray sweater has a soft feel. The oversized silhouette and low V-neck are perfect for layering over tees and blouses.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(68,'\"I believe in a product that is made with great craft, quality and creativity\", says Mr Brunello Cucinelli, and this shearling coat perfectly encapsulates his design ethos. It\'s cut for a generous length and has an incredibly supple, deep brown exterior which opens to a plush fuzzy lining – the insulating fabric makes it a luxurious addition to your cold-weather wardrobe. It\'s thoughtfully detailed with deep flap pockets and polished horn buttons.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(69,'Brunello Cucinelli\'s double-breasted coat is a contemporary take on the British naval officer\'s uniform. It has been tailored in Italy from a virgin wool and cashmere-blend. Though smart, it won\'t look out of place with a pair of selvedge jeans. Shown here with Brunello Cucinelli sweater, Brunello Cucinelli jeans, John Lobb boots.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(70,'Brunello Cucinelli\'s quilted gilet has been crafted in the label\'s factory in Solomeo, Italy. It\'s cut from lustrous shell and padded with feathers for optimum insulation. This surprisingly lightweight piece is designed with handy pockets - perfectly proportioned for holding your keys and phone.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(71,'Part of this season\'s most talked about collaboration, Vetements\' velour top is inspired by Juicy Couture\'s iconic tracksuits. It\'s blended with a generous amount of stretch to create a sculpting slim fit and has a neat funnel neckline and curved hem. Mirror the Spring \'17 runway by teaming yours with the coordinating track pants.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(72,'Vetements\' red track pants are part of a collaboration with Juicy Couture, and were one of the most talked about styles from the brand\'s Spring \'17 show during Paris couture week. Made from soft cotton-blend velour, this high-rise pair is intricately embellished with scores of Swarovski crystals to spell \'Juicy\' at the back. Recreate the runway look with the matching top.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(73,'First spotted on the label\'s Spring \'17 runway held at Paris\' Galeries Lafayette, Vetements\' coat is made in collaboration with expert tailors, Brioni. One of a series of oversized, boy-borrowed designs seen at the show, this piece has been cut in Italy from wool in a double-breasted silhouette and finished with frayed trims. Layer yours over a striped shirt.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(74,'Vetements\' Spring \'17 collection is made up of 18 collaborations with other brands. First spotted at the Galeries Lafayette show in Paris, this bomber is designed with Alpha Industries - the label behind Air Force and Navy jackets in the \'50s. It\'s cut from shell in an oversized silhouette and finished with a drawstring hood, ribbed trims and plenty of pockets. Wear it with the army-green outer showing or turn it inside out to highlight the black lining.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(75,'Vetements teamed up with a host of specialist brands for its Spring \'17 collection - this blazer is tailored in collaboration with Italian heritage label, Brioni. It\'s cut from navy wool for an oversized, boy-borrowed fit that\'s enhanced with dropped shoulders. Roll the cuffs to reveal the pinstriped lining, as styled on the Galeries Lafayette runway in Paris.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(76,'Vetements\' story starts with denim - in Fall \'15 Artistic Director Demna Gvasalia presented a pair of reworked vintage jeans that skyrocketed the label to success. Part of its Spring \'17 collaboration with Carhartt, this cropped white denim jumpsuit has graphic black stitching and an open back. Mirror the runway and style yours with boots.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(78,'\"We thought we\'d go straight to the brands who make all these things best, and ask to do something in our way with each one,\" says Vetements\' Mr Demna Gvasalia on his decision to create the Spring \'17 collection entirely collaboratively. These shorts created with Reebok put an off-kilter slant on classic sportswear.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(79,'\"There\'s something wilfully subversive about Vetements\" says The Journal, a statement to which these bold blue jeans attest. Created in collaboration with iconic American label Levi\'s, this hardy non-stretch denim pair is detailed with vertical stitching that runs up the legs and through the pockets for a cool patchwork effect.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(80,'Givenchy held its Spring \'17 show in the grounds of Paris\' Muséum National d\'Histoire Naturelle - strings of balloon lanterns helped light the evening setting. First spotted on the runway, this mini dress is cut from sculpting stretch-cady, with a sweetheart neckline and asymmetric hem. The internal satin cups provide coverage and support.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(81,'Givenchy\'s biker jacket is immaculately crafted from panels of black, red and white leather. This Italian-made piece is detailed with sporty moto-style quilted panels and sleek silver zips. It\'s fully lined and has a slim, cropped silhouette.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(82,'Givenchy\'s knee-length skirt is crafted from sculpting stretch-crepe. This piece is tailored to sit at your natural waist and falls to an asymmetric ruffled hem. Style it with a tucked-in blouse and bold sandals.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(83,'Givenchy\'s polo dress is made from black and white striped cotton-piqué. It\'s detailed with an orange appliqué inspired by ancient Egyptian symbols – a recurring theme from the Fall \'16 and Resort \'17 collections. Wear yours with block-heeled sandals or brogues.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(84,'Givenchy\'s dress is cut from pale blush silk-satin. This slip style has thick red grosgrain straps and delicate lace trims. Wear yours with sandals and neutral underpinnings.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(85,'Givenchy\'s jeans are printed with the label\'s signature stars across the back. This blue pair is cut from stretch-denim with a flattering low-rise fit and subtly faded for a lived-in look. Wear yours with a printed tee and brogues.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(86,'This blazer sees Givenchy put a typically outré spin on classic tailoring. It has been crafted in Italy from a soft wool and mohair-blend and is detailed with a chunky zipper that extends around the waist. The peak lapels and neat vent keep it looking sharp and sophisticated. Shown here with Givenchy trousers, Givenchy shirt, Givenchy shoes.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(87,'Raise the ante of your casual looks with Givenchy\'s graphic T-shirt. Designed in a collage of monetary motifs that resembles a camouflage print, it\'s made from pure cotton and cut in the brand\'s Columbian fit. Keep the rest of your look simple. Shown here with Givenchy jeans, Givenchy sneakers, Givenchy backpack.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(88,'Cut from cotton-jersey in Givenchy\'s oversized Columbian fit, this T-shirt is boldly patterned with the label\'s moniker at the front. The large block letters are printed with a rich marigold and light-blue sky, giving it an almost cinematic appeal. Keep the rest of your look monochrome.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(89,'In an uncomplicated, wearable way, Givenchy\'s sweatshirt reflects the label\'s dark, urban – and at times gothic – sensibility. It is cut from slouchy cotton-jersey backed in ultra-soft fleece. The bold white \'Judas\' appliqué is positioned dead centre, so it will be visible even with a coat or jacket over the top.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(90,'\"What I like to do is find ways to make menswear more interesting. It\'s about the area between suiting and sportswear, and it\'s about finding something new,\" says Givenchy\'s Creative Director, Mr Riccardo Tisci. A fine example of this approach, this blazer is made from robust black twill and finished with chunky canvas pockets for a tactile contrast. The unlined construction enhances its relaxed, modern feel.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(91,'Cut slim through the body and legs and with structured shoulders, this Givenchy suit has razor-sharp style. This design has a half-canvassed construction - a method of tailoring that delivers a superb drape and refined look. The grey cloth is woven from pure wool.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(92,'Gucci Creative Director Alessandro Michele creates collections that are a riot of color and decoration, and Spring \'17 takes this to another level. Made from tulle, these leggings are saturated with iridescent purple sequins that appear to dance beneath light. Replicate the runway by wearing yours with a printed top, or choose a sweatshirt for a look that\'s a little more effortless.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(93,'Presented at The Cloisters of Westminster Abbey, Gucci\'s Resort \'17 runway was inspired by Creative Director Alessandro Michele\'s first trip to London. Crafted from silk and wool-blend, this mini dress has red grosgrain ties and a ruffled bib and sleeves - a key detail in the collection. Layer yours with a metallic turtleneck and point-toe flats.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(94,'Gucci\'s mini dress has a pie-crust collar and ruffled trims for a romantic feel. Made in Italy from a navy wool-blend, it\'s decorated with lustrous faux pearl buttons and gold web stripes inspired by the label\'s equestrian roots - we like how they add definition to the shift silhouette. Complete your outfit with loafers.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(95,'Gucci\'s Cruise \'17 collection references art, interiors and British youth culture. This double-breasted coat is spun from wool in a classic red and black tartan, with yellow and white accents. It\'s punctuated by an appliquéd design at the back which reads \'Blind for Love\' and is surrounded by Staffordshire dog figurines - commonly placed on the mantelpiece of 19th century homes.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(96,'\"Michele\'s are clothes to live in, love in and play in, and most importantly, to be yourself in,\" says PORTER of Gucci\'s Creative Director\'s collections. Worn on the Resort \'17 runway, these skinny jeans are cut from dark-gray stretch-denim that\'s manually treated with chlorine for a bleached look. They\'re finished with floral and tiger appliqués - key motifs from the show.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(97,'Designed exclusively for MR PORTER. Gucci\'s \'Marco\' blazer is woven in a burgundy and navy houndstooth pattern – a nod to Creative Director Mr Alessandro Michele\'s appreciation of traditional tailoring. Crafted with touches of cotton for enhanced breathability, it has lightly padded shoulders, neat notch lapels and a single vent for ease of movement.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(98,'Designed exclusively for MR PORTER. Reminiscent of collegiate styles, this Gucci \'Cambridge\' blazer has been made in Italy from a slightly stretchy wool and cotton-blend. The deep navy shade is contrasted by red and green tipping - the brand\'s signature colours are instantly recognisable, but not garish.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(99,'Designed exclusively for MR PORTER. These Gucci trousers, like so much of the brand\'s output, defer to classic styles while wholeheartedly embracing the new. They\'re crafted from dark-green wool and trimmed along the seams with distinguishing velvet and satin piping - a reference to traditional military and dress trousers as well as sportier ones. Have the hems tailored with or without turn-ups.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(100,'Gucci\'s smart and sporty trousers are made from structured navy twill trimmed with white grosgrain stripes. The sweatpant-style drop-crotch shape is enhanced by elasticated cuffs, while the partially fitted waistband, belt loops, and concealed fastenings nod towards formal tailoring. Champion the brand\'s love of clashing colours and prints by pairing them with the floral shirt from the collection.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(101,'Make an assured declaration of good taste with Gucci\'s double-breasted overcoat. Crafted from pure cashmere in a timeless shade of tan, it has peak lapels and kissing buttoned cuffs for a refined look. The satin-twill lining is printed with vibrant blooms for unexpected flair.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(102,'These Gucci jeans are cut slim and stonewashed for a well-worn appearance and soft handle. Turn up the cuffs to show off the striped webbing detail - like selvedge edging it offers durability (and personality, too). Shown here with Gucci sweater, Gucci shirt, Gucci shoes, Gucci pouch.','Извините, описание отсутствует.'),(103,'black','Извините, описание отсутствует.');
